WEBVTT

00:00.265 --> 00:02.165
Previously on Breaking Bad...

00:02.175 --> 00:03.594
I can't help you get through this

00:03.605 --> 00:06.605
if you wont me what it is Walt did.

00:06.615 --> 00:09.935
Two men are coming to kill you.
Come again.

00:10.026 --> 00:11.746
Two men ambushed Hank.

00:11.862 --> 00:14.862
There tattoos indicate an affiliation
with the drug cartel.

00:15.022 --> 00:17.022
You knew my brother when
I was with the DEA.

00:17.486 --> 00:19.306
I investigate everyone I do business.

00:19.316 --> 00:23.436
I am sleeping with my boss
and I don't know why.

00:25.346 --> 00:27.166
What's up partner?

00:27.876 --> 00:29.196
This is my replacement?

00:30.784 --> 00:32.986
In the litlle village
<i>where I was born,</i>

00:33.020 --> 00:35.989
<i>life moved</i>
<i>at a slower pace...</i>

00:36.023 --> 00:39.726
<i>yet felt all the richer</i>
<i>for it.</i>

00:39.760 --> 00:43.563
<i>There, my two uncles</i>
<i>were known far and wide</i>

00:43.597 --> 00:45.999
<i>for their delicious cooking.</i>

00:46.033 --> 00:48.267
<i>They seasoned</i>
<i>their zesty chicken</i>

00:48.302 --> 00:52.038
<i>using only the freshest herbs</i>
<i>and spices.</i>

00:52.072 --> 00:55.475
<i>People called them</i>
<i>"Los Pollos Hermanos"--</i>

00:55.509 --> 00:57.477
<i>the Chicken Brothers.</i>

00:57.511 --> 01:00.213
<i>Today, we carry on</i>
<i>their tradition</i>

01:00.247 --> 01:03.449
<i>in a manner that would make</i>
<i>my uncleproud.</i>

01:03.484 --> 01:07.387
<i>The finest ingredients</i>
<i>are brought together</i>
<i>with loving care...</i>

01:07.421 --> 01:10.823
<i>then slow-cooked</i>
<i>to perfection.</i>

01:10.858 --> 01:14.460
<i>Yes, the old ways</i>
<i>are still best</i>

01:14.495 --> 01:16.629
<i>at Los Pollos Hermanos.</i>

01:16.664 --> 01:18.297
<i>But don't take</i>
<i>my word for it.</i>

01:18.332 --> 01:21.367
<i>One taste and you'll know.</i>

